Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:46.91,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在爱恋中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.33,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}万道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:53.67,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:57.84,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:10.63,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}话不投机 有些后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.58,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}流下眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:17.91,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}心随着急切的情感变乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:25.22,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}调整情绪 想知道真实的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:30.97,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}执着于达成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:34.65,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}重要的事物在不觉间模糊 溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:40.37,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}今天是崭新的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:45.80,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}全世界沉浸在爱恋中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:49.40,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}万道光芒 照亮心房
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:52.74,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}我想了解一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:56.83,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}说给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:06:00.46,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}一毫米的距离也觉得遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:03.53,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}匆匆走过的青春岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:07.80,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}不会忘 也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:10.56,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8}留下闪耀的一页
